{"tid":877124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報道：中聯辦法律部部長王振民下月離任","createTime":"2018-10-26T06:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T09:07:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a33ce95916e9eebf90187cbd3f86c6e2d3086b4a","tid":877124,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"有報道指，中聯辦法律部部長王振民十一月離任，返回清華大學法學院教書。<br />\n <br />\n據星島日報報道，52歲的王振民出任中聯辦法律部部長近3年，去年特首選舉結束後，曾表示未來五年未是合適時候重啟政改，要集中處理民生，否則社會或會變成如中東般內亂。他亦曾嘲諷經常攻擊中央及共產黨的人是「花崗岩頭腦」。<br />\n <br />\n報道又指，王振民有感於中聯辦法律部發揮空間不大，只負責宣傳憲法和《基本法》，加上無實權，而且晉升階梯、工作自由度不及內地，回內地發展空間可能更大。預料他會重返清華大學法學院任教，並在港澳《基本法》研究會、清華大學國家治理研究院等多個平台擔任要職。"},{"pid":"f2e6684fbda972533ae6b99607ae29bd17c12d0a","tid":877124,"uid":20815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:29:20.000Z","msg":"聞到燶味？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8173d7dfd2b95254fcf7c06d08bb1df4d350735","tid":877124,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:02:00.000Z","msg":"抑鬱地離任"},{"pid":"9e25ec2b30b5c60b8b01031fecf7844320353212","tid":877124,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔駛死囉"},{"pid":"305c4ac230d6ac17782ac78b59c1906185a363c4","tid":877124,"uid":21917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:13:55.000Z","msg":"自殺釋兵權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd255d8e50db87cc8b96a8559af1eefb74ecce5","tid":877124,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:17:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯下月離世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f618608fc389791ea3720eb668dc3682b45deafd","tid":877124,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"走得快一定有古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63965f27167c20d4dc3ca08cf48443c241